                                        Add more information to improve your profile visibility!
                                        <% } else if (completion < 80) { %>
                                            You're doing great! A few more details and you'll have a complete profile.
                                            <% } else { %>
                                                Excellent! Your profile is well-optimized.
                                                <% } %>
